1
00:00:49,375 --> 00:00:51,708
Follow my lead, boys.
We'll be home in time for dinner.

2
00:00:58,833 --> 00:01:01,583
Humans, we come in peace.

3
00:01:05,541 --> 00:01:06,624
...together.

4
00:01:06,625 --> 00:01:08,500
He's got a gun!

5
00:02:05,833 --> 00:02:07,750
Oh my God! Oh no. Oh my God!

6
00:02:22,958 --> 00:02:24,957
They're here! They're here!

7
00:02:24,958 --> 00:02:27,000
They're coming for all our asses!

8
00:02:31,708 --> 00:02:34,666
Wait! Wait! Take me! Take me!

9
00:03:10,416 --> 00:03:11,540
Teabag.

10
00:03:11,541 --> 00:03:13,291
Geronimo!

11
00:03:22,833 --> 00:03:26,375
Back to the moon with ya!

12
00:04:32,416 --> 00:04:33,333
No!

13
00:04:36,833 --> 00:04:38,083
All clear!

14
00:04:39,666 --> 00:04:41,333
Bases loaded, motherfuckers!

